===Etymology===
Area word; compare {{cog|my|ပြင်||to get ready; to prepare}}, {{cog|kac|hpra|tr=pʰraʔ³¹|t=to complete}}, {{cog|mnw|ပြေၚ်||to prepare; to arrange for}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

